      "content": "Be extremely cautious of the scope of \"Representatives\"—this term can sometimes be stretched to include subcontractors or partners you might not expect to be liable. Also, look closely at exclusions; sometimes NDAs carve out liabilities for the Disclosing Party, which might not apply in this specific indemnification clause. Finally, check if there are any limits or caps on liability elsewhere in the agreement to see if this clause is truly unlimited.",
